PROGRAM 6: Write a c program that reads an integer and float value and displays them 

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
int number;
float value ;
printf("Enter an integer");
scanf("%d",&number);

printf("Enter a float value");
scanf("%f",& value );
printf("\n---output---\n");
printf("integer : %d\n",number);
printf("float:%.2f\n",value);
return 0 ; 
}


OUTPUT 
Enter an integer28
Enter a float value28

---output---
integer : 28
float:28.00

[Process completed - press Enter]
